flowchart TD
  subgraph ClientSide
    Browser[Browser / User]
    CDN[Vercel CDN]
  end

  subgraph Frontend
    Vercel[Vercel - React (Vite) SPA]
  end

  subgraph Edge
    LB[Global Load Balancer / CDN]
  end

  subgraph Backend
    API[Render - Node/Express API]
    Auth[Azure AD (OIDC) / Microsoft Graph]
    Scheduler[GitHub Actions / Render Cron]
    Workers[Optional Background Workers]
  end

  subgraph Data
    Postgres[(Postgres DB)]
    MatViews[(Materialized Views)]
    Audit[Audit & Escalation Logs]
    FileStore[(Optional File Storage)]
  end

  subgraph Integrations
    SendGrid[SendGrid / SMTP]
    Monitoring[Monitoring / Logs]
    Secrets[Secrets Store (Render/Vercel/GitHub)]
  end

  %% Client to frontend
  Browser -->|HTTP(S) GET, SPA| CDN --> Vercel
  Vercel -->|API requests| LB

  %% Edge to API
  LB -->|HTTPS| API

  %% API components
  API -->|JWT / session| Postgres
  API -->|read-heavy analytics| MatViews
  API -->|write events| Audit
  API -->|uploads| FileStore
  API -->|email send| SendGrid
  API -->|auth redirect & token exchange| Auth

  %% Scheduler
  Scheduler -->|POST /api/admin/escalations/run| API
  Scheduler -->|POST /api/admin/analytics/refresh| API

  %% Workers
  Scheduler --> Workers
  Workers --> API
  Workers --> Postgres

  %% Data relationships
  MatViews -->|refresh based on base tables| Postgres
  Audit --> Postgres

  %% Observability & secrets
  API --> Monitoring
  SendGrid --> Monitoring
  Postgres --> Monitoring
  API --> Secrets
  Vercel --> Secrets

  classDef infra fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#0f172a,stroke-width:1px;
  class LB,API,Postgres,MatViews,Audit,SendGrid,Auth,Scheduler,Workers,Secrets,Monitoring infra;
